# Google OAuth Client ID
# How to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
#   2. Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID  →  Web application
#   3. Authorised JavaScript origins: add your Vercel domain (e.g. https://brandboard.vercel.app)
#      and http://localhost:5173 for local dev
#   4. Copy the Client ID below
#
# For production: add this variable in Vercel Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# For local dev:  copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com
